✅ Task 2: API Integration & JSON Handling
🎯 Goal
Learn how Python communicates with external APIs and handles JSON data.

📝 Requirements
Fetch data using Requests library
Parse JSON responses
Apply filtering or search logic
Handle API errors

💻 Description
In this task, I developed a Python application that fetches data from an external API and processes JSON responses using Python. The project demonstrates API integration, JSON parsing, filtering logic, and error handling.

